{"tid":2417750,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片][有錢佬係巴閉啲]  勞斯萊斯喺路中心跪低咗，大批交通狗/消防佬到場協助處理！","createTime":"2021-02-22T06:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T11:00:30.000Z","uid":121711,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fe49b2c48f53a83ffe0763a82e9db1b80bd80502","tid":2417750,"uid":121711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T06:26:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d-c4nk_kXno?t=15\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd-c4nk_kXno%3Ft%3D15&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY51QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=e445d832\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d-c4nk_kXno?t=15</a><br />\n<br />\n我頭先揸車經過堅拿道天橋，現場啲交通塞到仆街，喺塞車期間我見到大批交通狗，狗車，消防事故安全隊嘅車趕去現場，我心諗唔通前面發生咗大車禍？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我之後先發現，原來係因為前面有架勞斯萊斯喺路中心跪低咗，要call拖車到場處理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我屌你老母，壞咗架勞斯萊斯使唔使咁撚多差佬/消防佬過去招呼佢呀？巴撚閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n元朗721就唔見人，壞咗架勞斯萊斯就成大班差佬/消防趕住去現場報到，香港警隊果然係全世界其中一支最優秀嘅隊伍嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34be6d43809e5269961ca4372e2d8b0221898c49","tid":2417750,"uid":116696,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T06:30:27.000Z","msg":"著火喎Ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n著火你夠膽照行？"},{"pid":"8afe07d02b74d44cf1a869efa710cf0cb5434c90","tid":2417750,"uid":121711,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T06:37:58.000Z","msg":"係咪我打得飛機太多打到眼殘？請問段片入面邊度影到部勞斯萊斯著緊火？"},{"pid":"aaf1bbed2edcaaae268747c44181442f91f44972","tid":2417750,"uid":121711,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"34be6d43809e5269961ca4372e2d8b0221898c49","tid":2417750,"uid":116696,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T06:30:27.0